PrettyScript README
=============

  PrettyScript is a Ruby script parser.  You can get information
  by event-based style from the parser.

  !! WARNING !!

  PrettyScript is still early-alpha version.
  I never assure any kind of backward compatibility.
  
Requirements
------------

  * ruby 1.9 (support CVS HEAD only)
  * bison 1.28 or later (Other yaccs do not work)

Usage
-----

  See test/pscript/* and sample/pscript/*.

